cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with video summarization using deep learning methods, specifically a convolutional neural network (CNN). Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), and information retrieval, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper involves extensive training of the CNN, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
